Initialize the Database:Recreate the database:bash

cd ~/Downloads/Robotic-Sorting-System-main
rm -f src/database/sorting_log.db  # Remove old database
sqlite3 src/database/sorting_log.db < src/database/sorting_log.sql
sqlite3 src/database/sorting_log.db < src/database/sample_data.sql



Verify:

sqlite3 src/database/sorting_log.db "SELECT * FROM SortingLog;"

Expected:

1|2025-07-15 10:00:00|Red|Detected
2|2025-07-15 10:01:00|Blue|Detected
3|2025-07-15 10:02:00|None|Fault


Step 4: Recreate Sample Images

Ensure valid images:

sudo dnf install imagemagick
mkdir -p src/vision/sample_images
convert -size 100x100 xc:red src/vision/sample_images/red_block.jpg
convert -size 100x100 xc:blue src/vision/sample_images/blue_block.jpg


Verify:
file src/vision/sample_images/red_block.jpg

Step 6: Test the Streamlit Dashboard

cd ~/Downloads/Robotic-Sorting-System-main
source venv/bin/activate
streamlit run src/dashboard/app.py
